description: Try our easy to follow Breakfast Baked Egg Roll With Proscuitto & Cheddar recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Breakfast Baked Egg Roll With Proscuitto & Cheddar Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 100g roasted red capsicum, cut into strips

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat the oven to 180Â°C. Cut and discard the tops from bread rolls. Remove and discard the soft centre to make a shell. Line with prosciutto. Add a little of the cheese, then top with the capsicum. Crack an egg into each and top with the remaining cheese.
Place on a baking tray and cook for 10-12 minutes or until egg is cooked to your liking. Season with sea salt and cracked black pepper. Serve with baby rocket.
